2 CONC t;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font color="#0000a0"&gt;1848 - Petition presented to establish a Baptist Church in Leona, Leon County. Signed by Sentha Thomas, daughter of John and Phoebe Thomas. She was a member in 1850, decease
